## Conventions

- Every journey file is self-contained (readable without the others).
- Every visible step carries a stable id `J<tier>.<phase>-S<n>`.
- Every visible step carries a readiness chip.
- Every UI/terminal mock is wrapped in the `<!-- mock-begin: -->` / `<!-- mock-end: -->` envelope and extractable.
